Package: cellSight
Type: Package
Title: Pipeline to facilitate the downstream analysis of single cell experiment
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ranojoy Chatterjee, Chiraag Gohel, Ali Rahnavard
Maintainer: Ranojoy Chatterjee <ranojoy@gwu.edu>,Chiraag Gohel <chiraag@gwu.edu>, Ali Rahnavard <rahnavard@gwu.edu>
Description: The pipeline helps to streamline the down stream analysis of a single cell experiment
    It does standard filtering and qc plot followed by differential exprssion using tweedieverse
    an cell communication using cellchat.
